In [56]:
def margin(LTIs:list):    
    for LTI in LTIs:
        fig, ax = plt.subplots(2, 1)
        fig.set_size_inches(16,12)
        mag, phase, omega = lab.bode(LTI, dB=True)
        gm, pm, wcg, wcp = lab.margin(LTI)
        tit = "Gm={gm:.3f} dB (at {wcg:.3f} rad/sec), Pm= {pm:.3f} deg (at {wcp:.3f} rad/sec)".format(gm=gm, pm=pm, wcg=wcg, wcp=wcp)
        print(tit)
        gms = np.full_like(omega, gm,)
        wcgs = np.full_like(mag, wcg,)
        pms = np.full_like(omega, pm,)
        wcps = np.full_like(mag, wcp,)
        mag_dB = np.log10(mag)*20
        phase_degs = phase/ np.pi *180
        ax[0].set_title(tit, fontsize=12)
        ax[0].semilogx(omega, mag_dB)
        ax[0].plot(omega,gms, "r--")
        ax[0].plot(wcgs,mag_dB, "r--")
#ax[0].set_xlim(omega[0], omega[-1])
#ax[0].set_ylim(mag_dB[-1], mag_dB[0])
        ax[0].grid(which='major', color='#444', linewidth=1)
        ax[0].grid(which='minor', color='#aaa', ls=':')
        ax[0].set_ylabel('magnitude (dB)')

        ax[1].set_xlabel('Frequency (rad/sec)')
        ax[1].set_ylabel('Phase (deg)')
        ax[1].semilogx(omega, phase_degs)
        ax[1].plot(omega,pms, "r--")
        ax[1].plot(wcps,phase_degs, "r--")
        ax[1].set_xlim(omega[0], omega[-1])
        ax[1].set_ylim(phase_degs[-1], phase_degs[0])
        ax[1].grid(which='major', color='#444', linewidth=1)
        ax[1].grid(which='minor', color='#aaa', ls=':')
